<varlistentry id="options.DeskTopSize">
	<term>DeskTopSize <emphasis remap='I'>W x H</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>If <emphasis remap='I'>W</emphasis> or <emphasis remap='I'>H</emphasis> 
		are less or equal to 100 - they define number of rows and columns in virtual desktop,
		each sized same as the screen. Otherwise <emphasis remap='I'>W</emphasis> and 
		<emphasis remap='I'>H</emphasis> define the exact size of the virtual desktop in pixels, 
		but to be no less then the size of the screen.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
